A young and enthusiastic entrepreneur, Sarfaraz runs a garments shop in Karachi. He is 35 and married. He is gaining more experience with time and has improved his business a lot. He is organized and disciplined; 

Sarfaraz wants to boost his sales. For this purpose, he has requested a loan to get more established and improve his living standards.

He is very thankful to Kiva and field partner BRAC Pakistan.
